cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.AR, cs.SY 

This paper discusses the deployment of THz-APs in an indoor setting, which is related to networking (cs.NI) and information theory (cs.IT). The use of higher frequency bands for ultra-dense networks also involves multimedia (cs.MM) and architectural (cs.AR) considerations. Additionally, the proposed solutions for efficient packing of THz-APs involve system engineering (cs.SY) aspects.
